<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>理发会员管理系统</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary-color: #C9A067;
      --secondary-color: #F5F5F0;
      --accent-color: #B8860B;
      --light-color: #FAFAF5;
      --dark-color: #2C2C2C;
      --text-color: #3C3C3C;
      --text-light: #7C7C7C;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;
      color: var(--text-color);
      line-height: 1.6;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--light-color) 0%, #F0F0E8 100%);
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }
    
    ::selection {
      background: var(--primary-color);
      color: #2C2C2C;
    }
    
    .navbar {
      background: rgba(44, 44, 44, 0.98);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
      border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(201, 160, 103, 0.3);
    }
    
    .navbar-brand {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      color: #FAFAF5 !important;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    
    .nav-link {
      color: #E8E8E0 !important;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      padding: 8px 20px !important;
      border-radius: 20px;
      margin: 0 5px;
    }
    
    .nav-link:hover,
    .nav-link.active {
      color: #C9A067 !important;
      background-color: rgba(201, 160, 103, 0.15);
    }

    .nav-link.logout-link {
      color: #2C2C2C !important;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C9A067, #B8860B) !important;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(201, 160, 103, 0.4);
      font-weight: 600 !important;
    }

    .nav-link.logout-link:hover,
    .nav-link.logout-link:focus {
      color: #FAFAF5 !important;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #B8860B, #A0760A) !important;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(201, 160, 103, 0.5);
    }

    .nav-link.logout-link i {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    
    .hero-section {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2C2C2C 0%, #3C3C3C 50%, #2C2C2C 100%);
      padding: 90px 0;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .hero-section::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 80%, rgba(201, 160, 103, 0.25) 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 20%, rgba(201, 168, 123, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%);
    }
    
    .hero-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    
    .hero-section h1 {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
      color: #FAFAF5;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out;
    }
    
    .hero-section p {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 50px;
      color: #D8D8D0;
      animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.2s both;
    }
    
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C9A067, #B8860B);
      border: none;
      padding: 14px 36px;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 30px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 18px rgba(201, 160, 103, 0.45);
      color: #2C2C2C;
      animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.4s both;
    }
    
    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(201, 160, 103, 0.55);
      color: #FAFAF5;
    }
    
    .btn-outline-light {
      border: 2px solid var(--primary-color);
      color: #C9A067;
      padding: 12px 32px;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 30px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.6s both;
      background-color: transparent;
    }
    
    .btn-outline-light:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C9A067, #B8860B);
      color: #2C2C2C;
      border-color: transparent;
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(201, 160, 103, 0.45);
    }
    
    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(30px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }
    
    .features-section {
      padding: 90px 0;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #F0F0E8 0%, var(--light-color) 100%);
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .features-section h2 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 65px;
      color: var(--dark-color);
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .features-section h2::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -12px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 80px;
      height: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #C9A067, #B8860B);
      border-radius: 2px;
    }
    
    .dashboard-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 35px 25px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 22px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      transition: all 0.35s ease;
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(201, 160, 103, 0.1);
      min-height: 280px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .dashboard-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 4px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #C9A067, #B8860B);
    }
    
    .dashboard-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-12px);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
      border-color: rgba(201, 160, 103, 0.3);
    }
    
    .dashboard-card i {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
      color: var(--primary-color);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .dashboard-card:hover i {
      color: var(--accent-color);
      transform: scale(1.08);
    }
    
    .dashboard-card h5 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      color: var(--dark-color);
    }
    
    .dashboard-card p {
      color: var(--text-light);
      margin-bottom: 22px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    
    .dashboard-card .btn {
      background-color: white;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--primary-color);
      color: var(--dark-color);
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 25px;
      padding: 10px 28px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      align-self: center;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }
    
    .dashboard-card .btn:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C9A067, #B8860B);
      color: #2C2C2C;
      border-color: transparent;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(201, 160, 103, 0.4);
    }
    
    .footer {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2C2C2C, #3C3C3C);
      color: #D8D8D0;
      padding: 50px 0;
      margin-top: 70px;
      border-top: 2px solid rgba(201, 160, 103, 0.4);
    }
    
    .footer p {
      margin: 0;
      opacity: 0.8;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero-section {
        padding: 70px 0;
      }
      
      .hero-section h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
      
      .hero-section p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }
      
      .features-section {
        padding: 70px 0;
      }
      
      .features-section h2 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }
      
      .dashboard-card {
        margin-bottom: 25px;
        padding: 28px 20px;
      }
      
      .dashboard-card i {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
      }
      
      .footer {
        padding: 35px 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg">
    <div class="container">
      <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">理发会员管理系统</a>
      <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
        <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
      </button>
      <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
        <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="/">
              <i class="fas fa-home me-1"></i> 首页
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" href="/members">
              <i class="fas fa-users me-1"></i> 会员管理
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" href="/appointments">
              <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt me-1"></i> 预约管理
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" href="/transactions">
              <i class="fas fa-receipt me-1"></i> 消费记录
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" href="/orders">
              <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart me-1"></i> 订单管理
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" href="/balance">
              <i class="fas fa-wallet me-1"></i> 余额管理
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" href="/stats">
              <i class="fas fa-chart-bar me-1"></i> 数据统计
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link logout-link" href="/logout" onclick="return confirmAction(this, '确定要退出登录吗？', 'logout');">
              <i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt me-1"></i> 退出登录
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero-section">
    <div class="container text-center hero-content">
      <h1>欢迎使用理发会员管理系统</h1>
      <p>高效管理会员信息，预约和消费记录</p>
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-4">
        <a href="/members" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">管理会员</a>
        <a href="/appointments" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg">管理预约</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>系统功能</h2>
      <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div class="dashboard-card">
            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
            <h5>会员管理</h5>
            <p>添加、编辑、删除会员信息，管理会员档案</p>
            <a href="/members" class="btn">查看详情</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div class="dashboard-card">
            <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i>
            <h5>预约管理</h5>
            <p>管理会员预约信息，安排服务时间</p>
            <a href="/appointments" class="btn">查看详情</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div class="dashboard-card">
            <i class="fas fa-receipt"></i>
            <h5>消费记录</h5>
            <p>记录会员消费情况，自动计算积分</p>
            <a href="/transactions" class="btn">查看详情</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div class="dashboard-card">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i>
            <h5>数据统计</h5>
            <p>查看系统数据统计，分析营业情况</p>
            <a href="/stats" class="btn">查看详情</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div class="dashboard-card">
            <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i>
            <h5>订单管理</h5>
            <p>管理会员订单，查看订单详情</p>
            <a href="/orders" class="btn">查看详情</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div class="dashboard-card">
            <i class="fas fa-wallet"></i>
            <h5>余额管理</h5>
            <p>管理会员余额，支持充值和扣费</p>
            <a href="/balance" class="btn">查看详情</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <p>&copy; 2026 理发会员管理系统</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script src="/confirm.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>